{"tid":1557046,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家唔好停止跳閘","createTime":"2019-09-10T03:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T06:20:02.000Z","uid":291426,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2c412458ef5b82d29e5c39e0f4851acb66030ab4","tid":1557046,"uid":291426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"我都見到藍絲加警察濫權對付跳閘，風險係大左好多。無錯呀，而家係變相戒嚴，任何本身係低風險既行動都可以變得危險，包括跳閘，包括連儂牆，包括十點鳩嗌，包括和平示威<br />\n<br />\n要講清楚風險係無錯既，但係代唔代表有風險就唔好做呢？<br />\n<br />\n我明白行動要計算回報，但係抗爭行動好多時既回報都唔係即時或者直接，好似鳩嗌咁，無人會認為會令政權有任何壓力，但係絕對能夠互相打氣，如果一有危險就唔做（例如以噪音為由警察上門捉人），咁抗爭係無可能繼續<br />\n<br />\n極權必然會盡量將所有抗爭成本拉到有咁高得咁高，令啲人唔會再敢出聲為止。本身高危（前線）緊係要小心，但係其他人身家清白，<span style=\"color: red;\">應該係睇自己接受到幾多，要有心理準備佢有可能會煩你一段時間，係衡量過之後，應該繼續任何你認同既形式既抗爭</span><br />\n<br />\n否則白色恐怖係一定會越來越多"},{"pid":"54a118f767af84b6db2c46a46695eb3930689e6f","tid":1557046,"uid":2904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[全民和你唱</span></span>] 全世界全天候街邊唱香港國歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556100</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dd1d3264ae5efcc7cb8cd0772f2acf4c5fd70790","tid":1557046,"uid":143699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"老實講，其實跳閘大家都識，真係唔難。但困難嘅係要點要跨過自已嘅心理關口，一旦你跨過咗，跳閘對你嚟講真係easy job。<br />\n<br />\n我知道好多巴絲打都會擔心跳閘嘅時侯會被港鐵職員捉，驚會罰錢呀，又可能會犯法呀咁。但我想同大家講真係唔洗驚，因為係唔會架！你地睇完呢條片就知。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[全民乘搭港鐵優惠] <br />\n應對職員方法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yHVLw9-1k9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyHVLw9-1k9A&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDz1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=77a6d43b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yHVLw9-1k9A</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n優惠卷poster：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGZxvwU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGZxvwU.jpg&h=aa7704ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到今時今日，大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘。<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先我地重溫一下最基本嘅三種跳法先：</span></span><br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平日訓練：</span></span><br />\n大家可以係公園嘅呢啲健身器材到練習。其實正常人應該都做到動作一，你用呢個雙桿熟習下個動作，到落場跳就會輕鬆好多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSK69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSK69.jpg&h=21c80ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於動作二可以由低至高嘅障礙物慢慢練起，最緊要係起手動作，雙手配合身體擺動，跳起時心胸盡量貼緊膝頭<br />\n<br />\n動作三就周圍都練到，搵啲單邊嘅欄杆都得。同埋唔一定要單手，雙手都做到同樣效果。係冇咁有型姐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">注意事項：</span></span><br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">－最近黨鐵多咗狗，如果情況唔允許，希望大家都唔好勉強，可以改用老人卡。唔好因為咁而被人捉。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n完整跳閘教學示範片段： <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDz1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=74dca28c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"50372f8b7cc5455828a9e82c305b40b6faa1ab10","tid":1557046,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"跳閘對黨鐵係0損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81cd2d0524828f8365df7c7746565ae4d0b881a","tid":1557046,"uid":7516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"認同，有時有d野諗落好無謂，例如鳩叫，但做起上黎有一定效果，最起碼打氣之餘仲可以舒發情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19121e05e8e3d782141e3acc80eb9d5ce246454","tid":1557046,"uid":262263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:23:12.000Z","msg":"唔會停<br />\n太上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40144947cf4e038263b73298d56d07ae3fdd0299","tid":1557046,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:24:57.000Z","msg":"驚o既手足闊閘跟人出/入<br />\n唔洗跳 響機扮冇事"},{"pid":"1567152849760beda72259d8dfff81a50a86ca9b","tid":1557046,"uid":291426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50372f8b7cc5455828a9e82c305b40b6faa1ab10","tid":1557046,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"跳閘對黨鐵係0損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"無關係，從來唔係單一樣野會對佢有捐失，一定有多樣野（例如擺買所有黨鐵廣告既野）同時做，跳閘係要比所有人見到你對黨鐵既不滿（我都覺文宣係未講得好）<br />\n<br />\n咁當然，你可以接受幾大風險，覺得呢樣嘢有幾有意義，呢點每個人會有唔同判斷"},{"pid":"7649cd8d2e4c2dd2dc318dafb21a301d9dbb8463","tid":1557046,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b19121e05e8e3d782141e3acc80eb9d5ce246454","tid":1557046,"uid":262263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:23:12.000Z","msg":"唔會停<br />\n太上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c162da882e7867eac94785013ba065fbe8ea5d36","tid":1557046,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"跳完翻唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7b5690b7c3a96d9db149d8639942de086325dd","tid":1557046,"uid":283525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:40:22.000Z","msg":"停止跳閘"},{"pid":"c1cc0b4206e115e0c3fd6fc80f9caa89d0b66a07","tid":1557046,"uid":181436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:43:44.000Z","msg":"[重要!] 全部入黎!! 跳閘前必睇注意事項!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556898</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求留言幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"378f26c25e73721cfa005c4c080274fd86c8be85","tid":1557046,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>未爛未拆 咁樣入！</strong></span></span><br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmZ8JRV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmZ8JRV.gif&h=d48b36ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQ6rr7H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQ6rr7H.gif&h=2e882f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ch4X7sO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fch4X7sO.jpg&h=971c9013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDz1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=376cdf48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour <br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"c96e552a1097f8f661301f93d12dd9447e10e848","tid":1557046,"uid":4559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}